text:
In:
http://mail-archives.apache.org/mod_mbox/httpd-dev/200704.mbox/date

The 4th entry

Re: PATCH 19824 -- enhancement to mod_expires Sun, 01 Apr 2007 11:22:37 GMT

is duplicated; click on either, and the "Date >>" link refers to the same 
message, so it is not possible to use the link to move to the next message by 
date order.

The back links seem to work OK.
I don't know if there have been any updates to mod_mbox (or perhaps the mbox file has been cleaned up?) but the example works OK now.
creator: sebb@apache.org
